      "text": "あ、でも、このCMが流れて\n凄くいいことがあったんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-But‚ something really good happened\nbecause of this commercial!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
