      "text": "私のナレーションを聞いた学校の友達が\n「いくら断られても、めげずに遊びに誘うから！」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One of my friends from school heard my narration and said‚\n\"No matter how many times I'm turned down‚ I'll keep inviting you to hang out!\"",
